🌱 30-Day Beginner-Friendly Generative AI Study Plan
🎯 Daily Goals (Simple & Achievable)

Each day should feel like “I learned something useful,” not “I survived a storm.”

⏱️ Time Commitment: 1–2 hours/day
📘 Daily Structure:
Learn (30–40 mins)
Watch/Explore (20 mins)
Practice (30–40 mins)
Reflect (5–10 mins)
📅 WEEKLY BREAKDOWN
🟢 Week 1: Foundations of AI & Generative AI

Theme: Understanding the “brain” before using it

📚 Topics:
What is AI, ML, and Generative AI
Applications (Chatbots, Image Generation, Code Generation)
Basics of NLP (Natural Language Processing)
Introduction to LLMs (Large Language Models)
🎯 Daily Goals:
Day 1–2: Learn AI vs ML vs Gen AI
Day 3–4: Understand how text generation works
Day 5–6: Explore real-world use cases
Day 7: Revise + mini project
🛠️ Practice Tasks:
Write 5 real-life uses of Gen AI
Use ChatGPT to generate:
A story
A summary
Compare outputs with different prompts
